column2: Professional Holding Corp. engages in the provision of personal and corporate banking services. The company is headquartered in Coral Gables, Florida. The Bank conducts its banking operations from five branches and four loan production offices located exclusively in the Miami-Fort Lauderdale-West Palm Beach or Miami-Dade metropolitan statistical area (MSA), which encompasses three counties in Florida: Miami-Dade, Broward, and Palm Beach counties. The Bank offers its services to small to medium sized businesses, owners and operators of these businesses, and other professionals, entrepreneurs and high net worth individuals.
